## Component Specifications

### Notation Badge
- Dark background (#1A1A1A), white text
- Monospace font, compact padding (2px 8px)
- Square corners (border-radius: 0)
- Font size: var(--text-xs) (10px minimum)
- Variants: --sm, default, --lg

### Status Indicator
- Square dot (6px) + uppercase label
- Dot color matches status (monochromatic)
- Background: surface color
- Compact padding (2px 8px)
- Square corners

### Cards (Idea/Story/Sprint)
- Dense padding (16px, reduced from previous)
- Top border (3-4px) indicates status color
- Title, description (clamped to 3 lines)
- Meta footer with tight spacing
- Square corners (border-radius: 0)
- No shadows (or minimal 1px)
- Hover: border color change only

### Navigation
- Fixed position, 48px height (compact)
- Logo + notation badge left, links center, search right
- Links: uppercase, var(--text-xs), letter-spaced
- Tight spacing throughout
- Square corners on all elements

## Responsive Breakpoints

