## Anti-Patterns (Do NOT Do)

- ❌ Serif fonts (use sans-serif only)
- ❌ Text smaller than 10px
- ❌ Rounded corners (use square corners)
- ❌ Decorative shadows (minimal or none)
- ❌ Decorative colors or gradients
- ❌ Excessive whitespace
- ❌ Italic text (except citations)
- ❌ Centered body text
- ❌ Icons without labels in navigation
- ❌ Low-contrast text
- ❌ Saturated colors (use monochromatic palette)

## Density Guidelines

- Reduce padding/margins by 20-30% from typical web standards
- Tighten line-heights (1.2-1.4)
- Smaller font sizes where appropriate (maintain 10px minimum)
- Align all elements to grid
- Minimize gaps between elements
- Create density through typography and grid, not decoration
